items.title: Stock Radar: ICICI Bank, Waaree Energies, IndiGo, Inox Wind, DLF, Lodha, Bandhan Bank, Coal India, ITD Cementation in focus on Monday
items.description: Reliance Industries, Yes Bank, Bank of Baroda, Macrotech Developers, Intellect Design Arena, Praj Industries, Texmaco Rail, Balkrishna Industries, Torrent Pharma, CreditAccess Grameen, and Aegis Logistics will also be in focus on October 28.
